parameters: 実績を解放してなければ追加
"■■■は思い込みだけで■■できる■■になった。"
The power is on. It seems like we can go down below.
ロッカー内にあるイメージ

When I approached out of curiosity, I found something like a jewel
lying there. It seemed to be one of the beads that were probably
connected as a rosary.
演出：なんか、バグっぽくてこわくない？こういう繰り返し、という意図
繰り返さない場合はこんな感じかしらねぇ……

--There is something behind. Suddenly sensing it, I gulp
nervously.

Breathing--Body heat--I can feel those things. Without
getting closer, just being there. No--calling me? Being called. It is
calling out to me from behind.

What was there was a shadow. A shadow just standing
there, without doing anything... No, is it really standing there? I
can't see it clearly, I don't understand.
......Do you have something to tell me?

I try to speak, but there is no response. Judging from
the atmosphere emanating from the shadow, it is undoubtedly of the
evil spirit kind. However, strangely, I don't feel any malice.

......Make up one's mind. Take off the gloves and touch the
shadow.

The moment I touched it, it emitted a light, and before I
knew it, the shadow had completely disappeared.
......Courage, I whispered, and decided to move forward.

--How many times have I fallen into traps until now! There
is a flow of wind in this corridor, surely it leads to the next floor!
Let's break free just like this...!
